('98241','33883','5','Luxury villa in 1st sea line near Palma'),
('98242','33884','5','Only 5 minutes drive from Palma de Mallorca away sits this luxury villa in 1st sea line on a 2.000m² large plot. The villa has been extensively renovated in 2008. The approx 1.000m² living area is distributed on 2 residential floors and offers on the upper floor 6 bedrooms with bathrooms en suite. On the ground floor living-dining room, kitchen and access to the mediterranean garden with terraces and salt water pool aswell jacuzzi. Furthermore, this extraordinary Vila offers even a study room with lounge, 2 guest apartments with sep. access in the basement, 2 staff bedrooms, an indoor swimming pool with spa and gym and a home theater. All floors are connected with a lift. 5 cars fits in the garage in addition it still has outside car parking for 4 more cars. Facilities include central heating (gas, heat pump), air conditioning h / c, parquet floors, fireplace and an alarm system'),
